      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty is not formally assessed at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model is widely used for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction and is considered adequate for comparative assessment."
    },
